<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Email Verification - iListed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #18191a;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .code {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #18191a;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #999999;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>iListed</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>
      <p>Thank you for registering with iListed. Please use the verification code below to complete your sign-up process:</p>
      <p class="code">{{code}}</p>
      <p>This code will expire in 15 minutes.</p>
      <p>If you did not initiate this request, please ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br/>The iListed Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 iListed. All rights reserved.<br/>
      1234 Street Address, City, Country
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
